### Lesson 0007: database-backed list
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items

### Lesson 0007: database-backed detail
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/2

### Lesson 0008: create a persistent item
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Persistent FastAPI Notes",
  "category": "book",
  "price": 12.5,
  "in_stock": true
}

### Lesson 0008: query persisted items
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items?category=book
